    "title": "Now Hiring Store Manager at Costco India",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Store Manager with drive and ambition, Costco India in Kochi is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Costco India:\nCostco India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Costco India!",
